{"tid":1613793,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[預告被自殺] 西營盤榮基地産代理公司門前紅色欄杆","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:40:47.000Z","uid":190579,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7678a1ab7ed4af97f7e764607b2fb650770925bc","tid":1613793,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"時間：大概六點三<br />\n<br />\n地點：榮基地産代理公司門前紅色欄杆<br />\n西環德輔道西258號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LzmfSGj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLzmfSGj.png&h=64a31ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片係Google map街景，可能唔update<br />\n但報夢比我隻鬼話地點係榮基門口附近既紅色鐵欄<br />\n如有錯請街坊指正，我del post<br />\n<br />\n欄杆款式：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kcOtkh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kcOtkh.png&h=cf26aebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事發經過：<br />\n有三個軍裝警員並排企喺個欄杆度講嘢唔知講咩<br />\n捉住個欄杆輕力chok 幾下<br />\n向面前棟樓既樓上望<br />\n隻鬼隔半條街見到，以常人步速經過咗，D警察仲喺度<br />\n之後就唔知了<br />\n<br />\n劇本：<br />\n年輕男子跳樓自殺，跌落欄杆身體一分為二，死因冇可疑"},{"pid":"a91124c21376cb3f32e22c770f5fcf0c6b296099","tid":1613793,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b84f7100f861ebc46a1fc0c93d1fb8596be1dca2","tid":1613793,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:35:56.000Z","msg":"lm sin"},{"pid":"1ae120cdd460acff9b750b03630072c2a723a5be","tid":1613793,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8db3c46e5c4fe9316674af59e29f6f4f01a4b7","tid":1613793,"uid":41608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:39:10.000Z"